article_title: Some exchange health plans don’t include Hamilton, local doctors

article_metadata.author: Charles Olivercharlesoliver@daltoncitizen.com

og.description: Those who buy some health insurance plans on Georgia’s Obamacare exchange won’t get network access to Hamilton Medical Center and most local doctors.
